data.name: optBtnRendermax.ToolTip
data.value: Enables the dfhack plugin. You can always disable it while playing with "rendermax disable" in your dfhack window. Currently you can only have either Rendermax or TTF active and it requires print mode STANDARD.

data.name: optCbStartingLabors.ToolTip
data.value: You can have your dwarves start/arrive without any labor types enabled here by setting this to NO. You can also set it to SKILLS to make the labor list set by skill, or BY_UNIT_TYPE to have it done by overall unit type.
